schema.description: Properties apply to all supported country codes, except where specified.

customer.description:
Details of the customer making the purchase.

Details of the customer will need to be submitted to the service. No default values will be set.

firstName.description:
Customer's first name. 

Also known as Given Name(s).

lastName.description:
Customer's last name (Optional).

Also known as Family Name.

phoneNumber.description:
Customer's phone number.

A phone number can be represented in:
  - E.164 format e.g. +447777111111 or;
  - Local format of submitted tenant e.g. 07777111111.

E.164 formatted phone numbers are preferred.

fulfilment.description: How and when the items will be received by the customer.

location.description:
The destination the customer wants to receive the order.

This only applies to purchases with a delivery service type.

address.description: The postal address where the customer wants to receive the order.

administrativeArea.description:
Geographical region of this address. 

Also known as County or State.

Required in Australia (AU) only for an order to be fulfilled.

lines.description: One or more lines representing the street address.

items.description: Represents part of a street address.

locality.description:
The locality of this address.

Also known as Town or City.

geolocation.description:
The coordinates of a geographical location where the customer wants to receive the order.

Required in Australia (AU) and New Zealand (NZ) only for an order to be fulfilled.

latitude.description: The latitude of the geographical location.

longitude.description: The longitude of the geographical location.

time.description: Time the customer wants to receive the order i.e. when order is fulfilled.

asap.description:
If the order should be fulfilled as soon as possible (ASAP).

ASAP may not be fulfillable.

Default is false.

scheduled.description:
Scheduled time the customer wants the order to be fulfilled.

If ASAP is selected and fulfillable, this will be set to the next available fulfilment time.

from.description: Earliest time the customer wants the order to be fulfilled represented in ISO 8601 UTC (Zulu Time).

to.description:
Latest time the customer wants the order to be fulfilled represented in ISO 8601 UTC (Zulu Time). 

This time must be greater than or equal to the from time.

isFulfillable.description: Whether the proposed order can be placed.

issues.description: One or more issues associated the proposed order, that may impact whether it can be placed.

restaurant.description: The restaurant selling the items to be purchased.

availabilityId.description: Unique identifier to identify when item(s) are available for ordering.

serviceType.description: How the order will be dispatched.
